@startuml Sequence Diagram - Payment Processing
!define TITLE Sequence Diagram - Payment Processing
title TITLE

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #009900

actor Tenant
participant "Payment App" as PayApp
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Payment Service" as PayService
participant "Payment Gateway\n(Stripe/PayPal)" as PaymentGW
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as NotifService

Tenant -> PayApp: Initiate payment
PayApp -> Gateway: POST /payments/initiate
Gateway -> PayService: Create payment request
PayService -> DB: Store payment record (PENDING)
DB --> PayService: Payment ID
PayService --> Gateway: Payment ID & redirect URL
Gateway --> PayApp: Payment page URL
PayApp --> Tenant: Redirect to payment page

Tenant -> PaymentGW: Enter card details
PaymentGW -> PaymentGW: Validate card
PaymentGW -> PaymentGW: Tokenize payment
PaymentGW --> Tenant: Verification (OTP/3D Secure)

Tenant -> PaymentGW: Confirm verification
PaymentGW -> PaymentGW: Process charge
PaymentGW -> Gateway: Webhook: payment.success
Gateway -> PayService: Update payment status
PayService -> DB: Update payment (COMPLETED)
DB --> PayService: Updated
PayService -> NotifService: Send receipt
NotifService --> Tenant: Payment receipt (Email/SMS)
Gateway --> PaymentGW: Ack webhook

alt Payment Fails
PaymentGW -> Gateway: Webhook: payment.failed
Gateway -> PayService: Update payment status
PayService -> DB: Update payment (FAILED)
DB --> PayService: Updated
PayService -> NotifService: Send failure notification
NotifService --> Tenant: Payment failed message
end

PayService --> PayApp: Payment status
PayApp --> Tenant: Payment confirmation page

@enduml